Package: psmqte
Title: Propensity Score Matching for QTE, QTT, ATE, and ATT
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Li", "Lu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "llu@geneseo.edu")
  )
Description: Implements propensity-score matching estimators for quantile
    treatment effects (QTE), quantile treatment effects on the treated (QTT),
    average treatment effects (ATE), and average treatment effects on the
    treated (ATT). The package provides formula-based interfaces, nearest
    neighbor matching with replacement, feasible influence-function standard
    errors for QTE/QTT, matching diagnostics, and simulation helpers.
